headline: Zoetis Receives European Commission Marketing Authorization for Lenivia速 (izenivetmab) to Reduce Pain Associated with Osteoarthritis (OA) in Dogs
summary: PARSIPPANY, N.J., November 26, 2025--Zoetis Inc. today announced that the European Commission has granted the company marketing authorization for Lenivia速 (izenivetmab) for the reduction of pain associated with osteoarthritis (OA) in dogs.
